202
00:08:20.170 --> 00:08:23.210
Pesa mucho, articuló la sirvienta, sin dejar de

203
00:08:23.210 --> 00:08:23.850
temblar.

204
00:08:24.810 --> 00:08:26.250
Jordán lo levantó,

205
00:08:26.490 --> 00:08:27.370
pesaba

206
00:08:27.530 --> 00:08:28.170
extraordinariamente.

207
00:08:29.025 --> 00:08:31.185
Salieron con él, y sobre la mesa del

208
00:08:31.185 --> 00:08:33.825
